abstract: College Basketball Roundup; Indiana University beats St John's University, 83-73, in consolation round at Maui Invitational; other men's and women's scores noted.
lead_paragraph: Yogi Ferrell led No. 13 Indiana over St. John’s in the consolation round of the Maui Invitational.

headline.main: Indiana Fends Off St. John’s; Vanderbilt Reaches the Final
